{"tid":2367071,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"「桐叔」被帶走的一刻  「堅持！香港人不要放棄！」","createTime":"2021-01-15T05:06:44.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-15T05:15:22.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"acc36e554d60942e170b129ba2f9c2d80ea4f627","tid":2367071,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-15T05:06:44.000Z","msg":"#12港人 #黃國桐 #香港人堅持<br />\n<br />\n「桐叔」被帶走的一刻 <br />\n「堅持！香港人不要放棄！」<br />\nJan 14, 2021<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=GVOqG4coTXg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DGVOqG4coTXg&d=ZtPc16BOUua4x2eUEWBZFuoeOpwBOZOods3%2BbOb6780%3D&h=7f89c34c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=GVOqG4coTXg</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nRFA 自由亞洲粵語<br />\n202K subscribers<br />\n<br />\n多家港媒引消息報道，香港警務處國安處周四（14日）早上拘捕11人，包括8男3女，涉嫌「協助罪犯」，據悉涉及12港人案件，被捕者年齡介乎18至72歲。<br />\n<br />\n本身是律師的九龍城區議員黃國桐，社交專頁指國安處人員約清晨6時到其寓所。警方中午前帶黃國桐返回位於福佬村道的議員辦事處搜查，離開時黃國桐高呼口號，籲港人不要放棄─「堅持民主、法治、人權！香港人不要放棄！」<br />\n<br />\n黃國桐現年72歲，是反送中運動其中一名義務律師，為大批年輕抗爭者提供免費法律援助，有「桐叔」之稱。<br />\n<br />\n另外社運人士何潔泓也在社交平台表示，她的母親約6時被警察上門拘捕。<br />\n<br />\n(香港電台片段)<br />\n<br />\n#12港人<br />\n#黃國桐<br />\n#香港人堅持<br />\n#不要放棄<br />\n<br />\n--------------------------------------------------<br />\n<br />\n自由亞洲電台 (Radio Free Asia) 總部設在美國華盛頓，為言論自由受限的亞洲國家和地區提供完整而免費的新聞報道。致力以多媒體形式發送新聞，成為一個讓大眾獲得可靠消息的平台。<br />\n<br />\n--------------------------------------------------<br />\n<br />\n《訂閱自由亞洲電台粵語部頻道 》 <a href=\"http://www.youtube.com/subscription_c...\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fsubscription_c...&d=ZtPc16BOUua4x2eUEWBZFuoeOpwBOZOods3%2BbOb6780%3D&h=4c57d81b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.youtube.com/subscription_c...</a><br />\n<br />\n【官網】<a href=\"https://www.rfa.org/cantonese\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rfa.org%2Fcantonese&d=ZtPc16BOUua4x2eUEWBZFuoeOpwBOZOods3%2BbOb6780%3D&h=afe5a427\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.rfa.org/cantonese</a><br />\n【Instagram】@rfacantonese<br />\n【Twitter 推特】@RfaCantonese<br />\n【Facebook 臉書】<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/cantonese.rfa\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fcantonese.rfa&d=ZtPc16BOUua4x2eUEWBZFuoeOpwBOZOods3%2BbOb6780%3D&h=b220a4b9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/cantonese.rfa</a><br />\n【Google +】<a href=\"https://plus.google.com/+CantoneseRFA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fplus.google.com%2F%2BCantoneseRFA&d=ZtPc16BOUua4x2eUEWBZFuoeOpwBOZOods3%2BbOb6780%3D&h=4a5eacfe\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://plus.google.com/+CantoneseRFA</a><br />\n【YouTube】<a href=\"http://www.youtube.com/user/cantoneseRFA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fuser%2FcantoneseRFA&d=ZtPc16BOUua4x2eUEWBZFuoeOpwBOZOods3%2BbOb6780%3D&h=4f15d2a2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.youtube.com/user/cantoneseRFA</a><br />\n【SoundCloud】<a href=\"https://soundcloud.com/rfacantonese\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsoundcloud.com%2Frfacantonese&d=ZtPc16BOUua4x2eUEWBZFuoeOpwBOZOods3%2BbOb6780%3D&h=a25b15fc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://soundcloud.com/rfacantonese</a>"},{"pid":"62fb3526bdc0b55185983ddb4344f4327adc3855","tid":2367071,"uid":19640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-15T05:12:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" c